item.title: CVE-2022-4306|2024-08-03T01:34:50.052Z -- unknown -- panda%20pods%20repeater%20field
item.description: The Panda Pods Repeater Field WordPress plugin before 1.5.4 does not sanitize and escapes a parameter before outputting it back in the page, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against a user having at least Contributor permission.
